locations.description:
**Always Open:** ✔  
**Single Use:** ✘  
**Requirements:** 
- 1 x Paracord
- 1 x Red Rebel Ice Pick
- No body armor equipped

locations.title: SCAV Lands [ALL]
locations.description:
**Always Open:** ✔  
**Single Use:** ✘  
**Requirements:** Requires a player Scav and PMC to extract together

locations.title: Bunker Hermetic Door [All]
locations.description:
**Always Open:** ✔  
**Single Use:** ✘  
**Requirements:** Activate the [Hermetic Door Switch](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/reserve?locationIds=39277) (you then have 4 minutes to extract before needing to activate the switch again).

**Note:** Activating the lever has a chance to spawn Scav Raiders around the train station

locations.title: Armored Train [ALL]
locations.description:
**Always Open:** ✘  
**Single Use:** ✔  
**Requirements:** -

**Notes:** 
- Arrives between 25-35 minutes into the raid (20-10 minutes left)
- Stays for 7 minutes
- Honks twice on arrival
- Honks once 1 minute before departure
- Honks twice just before doors close

**Train Loot:**
- Weapon Box [6x3] - in the train carriage opposite the bunkers
- Grenade Box - in the train carriage opposite the bunkers, under a seat

locations.title: D-2 [PMC]
locations.description:
**Always Open:** ✔  
**Single Use:** ✘  
**Requirements:** Activate [the switch](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/reserve?locationIds=41029), then press the button beside the extract to exit.

locations.title: Hermetic Door Switch
locations.description:
Activate this switch to unlock the [Bunker Hermetic Door](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/reserve?locationIds=39336) extract for 4 minutes (after which the switch will need to be activated again).

**Note:** Activating the switch will sound an alarm and has a chance to spawn Scav Raiders around the train station.

Once you have retrieved the package, you must extract from the location and hand it over to Peacekeeper.
